This directory contains examples and solution programs from the book
A.K. Hartmann "The big practical guide to computer simulations"
(World Scientific, 2014).
For each chpater of the book, a subdirectory exists, as follows

directory      chapter
------------------------------------------------------------------
c-programming  Programming in C
scripts        Scripts
se             Software Engineering
debugging      Debugging and Testing
oop            Object-oriented Software Development
algorithms     Algorithms and data structures
libraries      Libraries
randomness     Randomness and Statistics
literature     Information Retrieval, Publishing and Presentations


